Package fr.sylfrey.misTiGriD.electricalGrid

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Aggregator
    Standard interface for grid aggregator services; a grid aggregator gets updated continuously by its prosuming children, cumulating all their prosumptions and prosuming the total from its own aggregator father.
    Lamp  
    OnOffProsumer  
    Prosumer
    Standard interface for any electricity prosuming appliance.
    RemoteAggregator
    Specific interface for remote aggregator, same functionality as Aggregator but with serialisable ActorRefs.
    Storage
    A Storage is a particular Prosumer that stores electricity it consumes while loading and returns it while unloading.
    TunableProsumer
    A Prosumer with a tunable prosumed power.
